Heat oil in large non-stick skillet on medium-high heat. Add chicken; cover. Cook 4 minutes on each side or until cooked through. Remove chicken from skillet. Add water, soup and nutmeg to skillet; stir. Bring to boil. Bring to boil. Stir in rice, spinach and cheese. Top with chicken; cover. Reduce heat to low; cook 5 minutes. Let sit 5 minutes.